{"tid":1601840,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際戰線] 美國首都華盛頓DC 2019/09/28 全球聲援香港集會","createTime":"2019-09-29T07:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T07:55:28.000Z","uid":126841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"80217bc2da770b63a35e6697d4ed017c065e2322","tid":1601840,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"大家好呀！！！小弟今日一早就起身刷咗個牙沖好涼換好衫就出咗門口。<br />\n因為今日對於香港人嚟講，係一日個好重要既日子。<br />\n<br />\n五年前既今日我企喺中環充滿愛與和平的路上影低呢張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDRWaim.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDRWaim.jpg&h=ba4a3894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到今時今日我企咗喺地球既叻一邊，做同一樣嘢：為香港<span style=\"color: red;\">未來</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">自由</span>與<span style=\"color: red;\">民主</span>企出來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkajSuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkajSuf.jpg&h=cac619ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姨姨好好人，佢一直都keep住舉牌，各每一位參加者同香港人講加油！我祝佢好人一世平安！身體健康！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺今日嘅集會入面，我地個個都好驚訝。因為有來自<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">中國</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">美國來自唔同州</span>既人都有黎參與！有一位姐姐唔係住喺美國，但係旅遊途中咁岩經過DC，決定過黎參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0SioAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0SioAR.jpg&h=bbdd9787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEMSs8O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEMSs8O.jpg&h=b5c64578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YOj8LWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYOj8LWz.jpg&h=b9f7ac62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢一家人來自North Carolina, 佢哋特登一早過嚟DC。從NC黎DC揸車最少都要兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦晒你哋！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志既成員 <span style=\"color: red;\">Nathan Law 羅冠聰</span> 同埋 <span style=\"color: red;\">Jeffrey Ngo 敖卓軒</span> 都黎咗DC參與集會！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Go5Pvgf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGo5Pvgf.jpg&h=79acca3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmoNg6P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmoNg6P.jpg&h=dddbc7ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋起咗好多塊連儂牆，差唔多塊塊都癡滿哂！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HLCN1nP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHLCN1nP.jpg&h=851c6250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有喜好日本文化嘅香港人幫我地整咗塊好特別嘅連儂牆，我哋摺紙接出白鴿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TodYoAO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTodYoAO.jpg&h=7385d31b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你有曾經去過美國領事館集會，可能你會見過呢塊Banner!!! 手足們將呢塊Banner特登從香港寄過黎美國俾我地舉！！！！我地都好開心見到咁靚嘅Banner!!!!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWewJBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWewJBc.jpg&h=db33e8c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyTtLPj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyTtLPj.jpg&h=bc0b606e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男神羅冠聰，敖卓軒及數位香港人都為香港人同參與者打氣！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RJy15PD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRJy15PD.jpg&h=1551a7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkPQeW5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkPQeW5.jpg&h=5abd2eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9XrK3QS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9XrK3QS.jpg&h=03ebf2db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VAaDoSq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVAaDoSq.jpg&h=34c38597&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4MmCEqT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4MmCEqT.jpg&h=aa157ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後完場，大合照一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6BGZSur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6BGZSur.jpg&h=03f369d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋今日大概有300人左右出席，由於我哋號召力冇其他地方咁強，所以號召唔到太多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於如果大家想知道美國國會最新嘅消息，可以隨時like我哋個Facebook page DC4HK 我哋嘅目的係向每一位客人發佈最新來自美國嘅消息！！<br />\n<br />\n我哋係一班係美國DC附近居住/讀書嘅香港人，我哋一直都好想幫香港手但係我哋做到嘅只有<span style=\"color: orange;\">約下美國國會議員叫佢哋支持香港人權及民主法案，出席係DC嘅聽證會，發起係DC嘅支持香港活動，幫忙做文宣向呢邊嘅美國人宣傳香港發生緊嘅事, etc</span><br />\n好多謝每一位很企出嚟嘅香港人，你哋係我哋心目中嘅英雄！！希望大家可以保持到呢團火！！！有任何困難唔好放棄！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bysycNb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbysycNb.jpg&h=6d997662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">P.S. 我就係你哋所講嘅死MK仔，美國國會聽證會坐係Sharon Hom媽媽後面果個。放心啦我會剪頭髮㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住我都知道我好干擾視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要屌就屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a80eed97be481604db8d1ffe571882bb8dec11f9","tid":1601840,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:46:59.000Z","msg":"到今時今日我企咗喺地球既<span style=\"color: red;\">另</span>一邊，做同一樣嘢：為香港<span style=\"color: red;\">未來</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">自由</span>與<span style=\"color: red;\">民主</span>企出來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkajSuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkajSuf.jpg&h=cac619ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姨姨好好人，佢一直都keep住舉牌，各每一位參加者同香港人講加油！我祝佢好人一世平安！身體健康！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e2c364d599360db75a28370d29decc730d1f5a","tid":1601840,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:48:03.000Z","msg":"推一推～～"},{"pid":"08c7d1b5e4bf607977cc088eddd20f46d232af84","tid":1601840,"uid":259732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:48:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"015822414e08cda49c31181b86eca4750ac29ea4","tid":1601840,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"4f65c8bce93a14543a6ecb060f9f1131b230b314","tid":1601840,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"015822414e08cda49c31181b86eca4750ac29ea4","tid":1601840,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"ac9d366c11eba11171af2a9ff958ea1737d97873","tid":1601840,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f65c8bce93a14543a6ecb060f9f1131b230b314","tid":1601840,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"015822414e08cda49c31181b86eca4750ac29ea4","tid":1601840,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2